column5: Has anyone fished this area recently? I've never been there before and have heard good things about the area. Any info would be great.   PM me if you want.
No reports.. but possession is Zero until feb 8th.. one line only at all times.
Really? That's a weird date, I wonder why? (especially considering you're fishing for pen reared escapees)
bows are open wayne.  season & possesion is for lakers.
Whoa,  Wait a minute.  Escapees?  More, please.........
Lakers on my mind Raf ! lol... yah what Raf said.. and still one line only.
